[{"Id": 1011190, "EnglishTitle": "Eve of 18th Zilhijjah", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "18th Zilhijjah ki shab", "UrduTitle": "۱۸؍ذی الحجہ کی رات", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011868, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Sayyid Ibn Tawus, in al-Iqbal, has mentioned that on the night of Ghadeer, it is recommended to recite 12 rakat namaz jointly (12 rakats together). Only Tashahud has to be recited after the 2nd Sajdah of 2nd, 4th, 6th, 8th and 10th rakat. In each rakat (except the 12th rakat) after <Surah Fateha>, recite <Surah Ikhlaas>, 10 times and <Aayatul Kursi> once. In the 12th rakat, recite <Surah Fateha> and <Surah Ikhlaas> 7 times and in Qunoot recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Yeh Eid Ghadeer ki raat jo badi izzat o azmat ki haamil hai. Sayyad Ibne Tawus ne kitaab Iqbal mein is raat ki 12 rakat namaz ka zikr kiya hai jise ek salaam mein khatm karna hai (yaani 2x2 rakat karke nahi padhna hai, puri 12 rakat ek saath padhe aur aaklhri (12th) rakat mein salaam padh kar namaz tamaam kare). Is namaz mein Tashahud ko 2nd, 4th, 6th, 8th, 10th rakat ke 2nd Sajdeh ke baad anjaam diya jaaye. Har rakat mein (siwaaye 12th rakat ke) <Surah Fateha> ke baad 10 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> aur 1 martaba <Aayatul Kursi> padhe aur 12th rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad 7 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe aur Qunoot mein yeh padhe…", "UrduDescription": "یہ عیدِ غدیر کی رات ہے جو بڑی عزّت و عظمت کی حامل ہے،سیدؒ نے کتاب اقبال میں اس رات کی ۱۲ رکعت نماز ذ کاذکر کیا ہے۔ اس نماز کی ترکیب اس طرح سے ہے کہ یہ ۱۲ رکعت ایک سلام سے پڑھی جائے گی اور اس میں تشہد ۲، ۴، ۶، ۸ اور ۱۰ رکعت کے دسرے سجدہ کے بعد انجام دیا جائے۔ اس کی ہر رکعت میں (سوائے بارویں رکعت کے) <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۱۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> اور ایک مرتبہ <آیت الکرسی> پڑھے اور بارویں رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد ۷ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے اور قنوت میں یہ پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "