"GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "After completing the namaz go in prostration (Sajdah) and say the following 10 times…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Namaz tamaam karne ke baad sajdeh mein ja kar 10 martaba is tarah se kahe…", "UrduDescription": "نماز تمام کرنے کے بعد سجدہ میں جا کر ۱۰ مرتبہ اس طرح سے کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011871, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to Him whose Knowledge encompasses everything. Glory be to Him that glorifications befit none but Him. Glory be to the Lord of Favors and Blessings. Glory be to the Lord of Nobility and Bestowals. Glory be to the Lord of Honour and Generosity. I ask You by the juncture of the Might of Your Throne, and the Ultimate Mercy from Your Book. And I ask You by Your Grand Name and by Your Perfect Words, that You bestow Your Blessings on Your Messenger Muhammad and his Progeny the Purified and accept my prayers. Verily You are the hearer and responsive of prayer.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Paak hai Woh jo har cheez ki ta’daad ka ilm rakhta hai. Paak hai Woh jis ke alaawa koi aur laayaqe tasbeeh nahi. Paak hai Woh jo saahebe ehsaan o neymat hai. Paak hai Woh jo saahebe fazl o ehsaan hai. Paak hai Woh jo saahebe izzat o karam hai. Mai sawaal karta hu Tere arsh ke buland maqamaat, Teri kitaab ki intehaayi rehmat aur Tere Isme Aazam aur Tere kaamil kalemaat, keh Tu rehmat naazil farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Ahlebait (a.s) par jo tayyab o taahir hai aur meri haajaat ko pura kar, be-shak Tu soonne waala aur qabool karne waala hai.", "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "SUBHAANA MAN AHSAA KULLO SHAIY-IN I’LMO-HU. SUBHAANA MAN LAA YAN-BA-GHIT TASBEE-HE ILLAA LAHU, SUBHAANA ZIL MANNE WAN-NE’ME, SUBHAANA ZIL FAZLE WAT-TAWLE, SUBHAANA ZIL I’ZZA-TE WAL KARAME. AS-ALOKA BE-MA-A’-QE-DIL I’ZZE MIN A’R-SHE-KA, WA MUNTA-HAR RAHMA-TE MIN KETAABE-KA, WA BIL-IS-MIL A’ZAME WA KALE-MAATE-KAT TAA-MATE AN TO-SALLYA A’LAA MOHAMMADIN RASOOLE-KA WA AHLE BAIYTE-HIT TAIYYE-BI-NAT TAAHE-REENA WA AN TAF-A’LA BEE KAZAA KAZAA, INNA-KA SAMEE-O’ON MOJEE-BOON.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ مَنْ اَحْصٰى كُلُّ شَیْءٍ عِلْمُهٗ، سُبْحَانَ مَنْ لَا يَنْبَغِى التَّسْبِيْحَ اِلَّا لَهٗ، سُبْحَانَ ذِى الْمَنِّ وَالنِّعَمِ، سُبْحَانَ ذِى الْفَضْلِ وَالطَّوْلِ، سُبْحَانَ ذِى الْعِزَّةِ وَالْكَرَمِ۔ اَسْأَلُكَ بِمَعَاقِدِ الْعِزِّ مِنْ عَرْشِكَ، وَمُنْتَهَى الرَّحْمَةِ مِنْ كِتَابِكَ، وَبِالْاِسْمِ الْاَعْظَمِ وَكَلِمَاتِكَ التَّامَةِ اَنْ تُصَلِّىَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ رَسُوْلِكَ وَاَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ وَاَنْ تَفْعَلَ بِىْ كَذَا كَذَا، اِنَّكَ سَمِيْعٌ مُجِيْبٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "